This option tracks the part where an instance of java.lang.Thread class is generated and records it as transaction profile information.

Note that this option tracks the time when an instance is created, not when the instance is run. 

When this option is activated, you can see the following log in the log file.

    ...
    4/28/2015/12:04:27 PM Agent Control Module initialized(-8803105291542107178)
    4/28/2015/12:04:27 PM Agent Control Module loading complete... 
    ...
    2015-04-28/12:04:27 [I002] RT Class redefine java.lang.Thread
    ...

---

* Default value: true
* Format: Boolean
* Restart: Required
* Supported version: 5.0.0